    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-802b-b89f-e34e5b81a5dc",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "KT is difficult to do in scenarios where the opportunities for practice are small, such as big-block coding exercises. The authors propose 2 knowledge tracing models and a novel metric (Approaching Index Sequence). The programming path is represented by AISeq or AIScore (average of AISeq):",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-802b-b89f-e34e5b81a5dc",
        "parent": {
