    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80c0-b97e-f683e1631b3e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Both models are tested on two programming datasets, and the models were competitive with four state-of-the-art models on Precision-Recall, Accuracy, Specificity and Cohen’s Kappa. On a more fine-grained level, the models exhibited robustness in identifying students who fail to complete tasks.",
